Value NETWORK ([0-9A-Fa-f:]+::/\d+|[0-9A-Fa-f:]+/\d+)
Value PROTOCOL (\S+)
Value NEXTHOP_IP ([0-9A-Fa-f:]+|::)
Value PREFERENCE (\d+)
Value INTERFACE (\S+)
Value COST (\d+)

Start
  ^Destination\s*: -> Continue.Record
  ^Destinations\s+:\s+\d+\s+Routes\s+:\s+\d+\s+
  ^Destination\s*:\s+${NETWORK}\s+Protocol\s+:\s+${PROTOCOL}\s*$$
  ^NextHop\s+:\s+${NEXTHOP_IP}\s+Preference\s*:\s+${PREFERENCE}\s*$$
  ^Interface\s+:\s+${INTERFACE}\s+Cost\s+:\s+${COST}\s*$$
  ^\s*$$